org.insight_centre.aceis.eventmodel

Class EventPattern

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.insight_centre.aceis.eventmodel.EventPattern
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<EventPattern>

    public class EventPattern
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<EventPattern>
    An event pattern is the data model describing the correlations of the member events of a complex event. It also provides operations related to canonical event pattern creation and event pattern modification etc.
    Author:
    feng
